rows.label: qst200710_msg0001
rows.name:
You lot?!
Why in darnation are you here?!

rows.label: qst200710_msg0002
rows.name:
You're the one who told us to get
the Emperor's underpants, remember?

rows.label: qst200710_msg0004
rows.name: Yumyum is trying to sneak inside, duh!

rows.label: qst200710_msg0005
rows.name:
You lot can just stay here and talk
the guards' ears off.

rows.label: qst200710_msg0006
rows.name:
...Hm, yeah, those guards don't look
like they'd be easily convinced.

rows.label: qst200710_msg0007
rows.name:
Could Idaten get goods without
being spotted?

rows.label: qst200710_msg0018
rows.name:
It's more difficult than I thought...
At this speed, the guards'll see me!

rows.label: qst200710_msg0012
rows.name:
Well, whatever. Even if Idaten can't
do it, as long as we've got Meleph, we
should be able to just walk in, right?

rows.label: qst200710_msg0014
rows.name:
...I can get us in, but I'll admit
I'm not overly eager.

rows.label: qst200710_msg0015
rows.name:
To begin with, a sister stealing her little
brother's underwear...? It's just weird.

rows.label: qst200710_msg0016
rows.name:
Now, now. Don't be like that.
We're doing it for Idaten, right?

rows.label: qst200710_msg0017
rows.name:
...If you say so.
I can't believe I'm doing this...
